data.description:
ASSUMABLE 3.95% mortgage!

Charming 1 story home located nearby many in-town amenities! HUGE Fenced Backyard on a corner lot! The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 1 stall attached garage. Functional main level layout features living room, kitchen, dedicated dining room, 2 bedrooms, & bathroom located nearby! Finished basement features large bedroom (just needs egress), all utilities including laundry and tons of room for storage. Don't miss out, get your showing scheduled today!
